    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_7393367224471796224.png",
                "id": "talent30183",
                "key": "拂金劍鬥術",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "拂金劍鬥術"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">淨焰劍獄領域</span>；如果已存在淨焰劍獄領域，就先造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/862a5d3d2d4443f7f5068402b95c43c7_310330119216659172.png",
                "id": "talent12849",
                "key": "熔鐵流獄",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "熔鐵流獄"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>，然後<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備技能</span>：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">焚落踢</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">焚落踢</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/0a9de135471ab849dba578dcf95ebb6d_4922029695710287338.png",
                "id": "talent16022",
                "key": "炎嘯獅子咬",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "炎嘯獅子咬"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">當此召喚物在場且迪希雅在我方後臺，我方出戰角色受到傷害時：</span>抵消1點傷害；然後，如果迪希雅生命值至少為7，則對其造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>。（每回合1次）</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2870137020330467147.png",
                "id": "talent36574",
                "key": "淨焰劍獄領域",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/d85d7163eca60bd55a1624838144701a_3933212799554932770.png",
                "title": "淨焰劍獄領域"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_5808519406242797484.png",
                "id": "talent91878",
                "key": "火元素傷害‧其一",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素傷害‧其一"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\"><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">燃燒烈焰</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數：1，最多叠加到2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_7947158839506830259.png",
                "id": "talent89830",
                "key": "火元素傷害‧其二",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/3c3362a64ac984342133762388c9eb41_4851905222362429581.png",
                "title": "火元素傷害‧其二"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理傷害</span></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次可用次數；</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">準備技能</span></p><p>有些技能無法被直接使用，而是需要一定次數的行動輪來進行準備。</p><p>輪到一位牌手行動時，如果該牌手的「出戰角色」正在準備技能，則跳過該牌手的行動；如果技能已經完成準備，角色將會在此時直接使用此技能。（此類需要準備的技能，無法觸發「使用技能後」效果。）</p><p>只有「出戰角色」才能準備技能；如果正在準備技能的「出戰角色」被切換到後台，技能的準備就會被打斷。</p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/29/125391187/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_2305973163855144676.png",
                "id": "talent63562",
                "key": "規則解釋",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "規則解釋"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
